&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the strategy and technical direction for Apptegy&#39;s production databases hosted in AWS, including PostgreSQL, and other relational database systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the database layer of Apptegy&#39;s self-service internal developer platform, defining the guardrails that let engineering pods provision, monitor, and operate their own databases safely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive our high-availability, disaster recovery, and corruption-recovery programs, including DR and point-in-time-recovery drill cadence and RTO/RPO targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set performance strategy across the domain and coach engineers on advanced query tuning, transaction isolation, and execution plan analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own schema and migration governance across teams, advising on data models, database migrations, and application data access strategies to ensure long-term performance and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and automate operational processes for provisioning, maintenance, monitoring, and recovery.&lt;/li&gt;
